channel.title: Empire's Origin 525 - Rebuild (Best 525 Out)
channel.description:
[color=limegreen][center][move][size=30pt][shadow=red,left][font=Garamond]Empire's Origin 525[/font][/shadow][/size][/move] [color=black] ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/mcf4ap.jpg[/img] Introduction- The main aim of this server is to create a stable, decent and enjoyable server, with both Player vs Player, Player vs NPC and Skilling properties. This is a repost of Project Volcanic Stability. (Because I've updated it more, and the last project thread had a bad layout) When i mean decent, I mean nice economy, no customs items, npcs, clients. Something to as close to RS2 as a private server needs to be. Base~ Rs2hd "Aim of Server" I plan on making a fun and playable server that has both stability and a decent economy. Since I’ve realised many servers are going more and more away from the RuneScape theme, they're making a full on player killing server, which gets boring... I hope I stay with this project and produce something worthwhile. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Update Log~ 1/5/2009- Started Project. 1/5/2009- Made commands load from one file. 1/5/2009- Added Banking, (Withdraw 1,5,10,All) Gathered a few packets. 2/5/2009- HD and LD Support. (Fullscreen tabs are fuctional, updating client to fullscreen) 2/5/2009- Added leveling up interface, level information screens - [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2h6d2sg.jpg[/img] Added skill requirements. Added weapon requirements. 5/5/2009- Transferred RS2HD 3 way combat system. Working on NPC Combat (Begins) 7/5/2009- NPC Combat complete! Defence animations and hits. (Not fully) Specials work on NPCs. Only melee yet. 8/5/2009- Added private messaging frames Added Ignoring. Picture in thread somewhere! Added private messaging. [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/keitd2.jpg[/img] 10/5/2009- Started PvP, (Transferred base helped lots) Defence animations for players and special effects, equipment bonuses. Added skulling head icon - [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/10rk93p.jpg[/img] Fixed ground item, a bug appeared. [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2zdvqt0.jpg[/img] 14/5/2009- Added customising charecter, with saving. Will add to appearance change mage. 15/5/2009- Started ranged. Added arrow drawbacks and almost done with projectiles. [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/692tya.jpg[/img] Finished projectiles. Working on arrow detection and deletion. 17/5/2009- Working on trading, efficient base, every button working including X. (Added available spaces thing, these pictures are outdated) 2nd trade screen - Shows items, fixing the commands and trading with unknown is easy. Above pictures are outdated! 18/5/2009- Added NPC and Player dialouge (Fixed the head glitch - head would appear out of helmet. [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/16hqidj.jpg[/img] Working on mining and smithing now, because they're my favourite skills! 19/5/2009- Added Shopping, need someone to dump item prices... [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/295zwhz.jpg[/img] And. [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/j97b06.jpg[/img] 24/5/09 More information on Woodcutting~ [ul][*]Higher woodcutting level, faster logs collecting. [*]Sends message when logs cut. [*]Better the axe, higher chances of faster woodcutting. [*]Trees level requirements. [*]Axe level requirements.[/ul] 26/5/09- Began cooking, more information further in the thread, [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2yto278.jpg[/img] And~ [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/21nhces.jpg[/img] Cooking work with fires, ranges, most objects i've came across worldwide. Had delays between cooking, and also corrent experience per item cooked.[ 27/5/09- Began Fishing. Features~ [ul][*]Catches fish, depending on your fishing level. [*]Correct fishing level requirements. [*]Correct fishing tool requirements (Rod, Lobster Pot) [*]Different emote for different fishes caught. [*]Correct RuneScape experience. (May edit) [*]All uses events. As all my skills. [*]Working fishing items, (Such as gloves which increase fishing experience) [*]Obvious but auto-fishes...[/ul] I don't know i still may be missing something. So it isn't complete. [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/w9e16c.jpg[/img] And- [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/30ubsia.jpg[/img] 28/5/09- Also began Smithing. Started with Smelting. [ul][*]Iron Ores have effect of not being turned into Bars. [*]All Ores have been added, with correct experience from each one. [*]Uses event system.[/ul] That's it from Smithing so far. [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/33ngrbq.jpg[/img] ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- "Project Programmers" ~Origin ~Neji (Co-Developer) I don't plan on taking anyone in, sorry. I've realised that team projects sometimes don't work out, unless you know the person's talents and background. This source however will be released to public when completed or might be hosted for pubic play. Neji, is just helping, he's doesn't have full permissions. "Conclusion" This is a server which realises both the needs of the players and the needs of the server on the whole, it'll bring a revolution to 525's and continue the stability of rs2hd.[/SPOILER] "Requests/Help" Item price dumps, from the Grand Exchange database, Thank you![/SPOILER] "Suggestions" If you'd like to suggest something, complain on something feel free. I'm always happy to hear points of view.[/SPOILER] "Server Website" The server website will only have information about the server. It will host updates and future development. Made~ Getting Permission. "Forum" You're here! [IMG]http://www5.picturepush.com/photo/a/2120033/img/2120033.png[/img] I support Empire's Origin. [/center] [center]
~Support Signature~ [IMG]http://i28.tinypic.com/mcf4ap.jpg[/img]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Continued... Woodcutting picture. From above, ran out of space. [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/abtoya.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/258pkzl.jpg[/img] Coverted Graham's rs2hd's NPC vs NPC Combat. 100% credits to Graham 13/6/09- Magic on NPC. Details~ [ul][*]"Splashes" on dragons for time to time [*]Some spells hit more on certain monsters [*]Projectiles [*]All Modern and some Ancient spells[/ul] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/200p7op.jpg[/img] 16/6/09- NPC vs Player Details~ [ul][*]NPC Faces [*]Following, and Retaliation [*]Correct Defence Bonuses[/ul] Working on Aggression. [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/28rcm82.jpg[/img] Working Following, NPC Attack/Defence/Death Animations. Tormented Demon. Started on NPC Bosses/Team Events. [IMG]http://i595.photobucket.com/albums/tt31/originalpker/TormentedDemon.gif[/img] ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Videos - [URL=http://tinypic.com/r/166awxk/3]Ranging video - Projectiles, Player Killing[/URL] Player killing Clips - [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/b7m74o.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/2jbk2gw.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i595.photobucket.com/albums/tt31/originalpker/capture-1.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i595.photobucket.com/albums/tt31/originalpker/CombatThree-1.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i595.photobucket.com/albums/tt31/originalpker/CombatTwo.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/2yzbkon.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/295uyr4.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/savf9x.gif[/img][/SPOIL] Godwars preview - [IMG]http://i27.tinypic.com/2h2pjyg.gif[/img] King black dragon preview - [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/34he91g.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i26.tinypic.com/2woyumg.jpg[/img] Revenants preview - [IMG]http://i29.tinypic.com/9fxkev.jpg[/img] Features - * Teleblocking * Maging * Ranging * Freezing - Anyone know emote, when you're hit Summoning preview - [IMG]http://i32.tinypic.com/fd96ox.gif[/img] Reserved this post for updates.[/center][br][br][size=1]Posted on: September 01, 2009, 09:06:07 am[/size][hr]If you want the forums link, private message me. You'll get more info there, it's not out yet, BETA will be out soon. Originalpker~
